# Manual Test Cases

This folder contains examples of **manual test cases** created as part of my QA testing portfolio.

The test cases demonstrate structured test design for a public web platform signup and login flow.

Test design techniques used:

* Positive testing
* Negative testing
* Boundary Value Analysis
* Validation testing
* Security scenarios

The test cases include:

* user registration validation
* login validation
* age boundary testing
* account lock security scenario

The full test cases were designed using Google Sheets and exported as a PDF.
